{"doc":{"isMarkdown":true,"isTranslated":true,"isActive":true,"flaws":{},"title":"網站表單-與數據合作","mdn_url":"/zh-TW/docs/Learn/Forms","locale":"zh-TW","native":"正體中文 (繁體)","sidebarHTML":"","body":[{"type":"prose","value":{"id":null,"title":null,"isH3":false,"content":"<p>這篇指南提供了一系列的文章，幫你掌握 HTML 表單的基本知識。對於與使用者互動，網站表單是一項十分有力的工具，最常使用於用戶數據蒐集，或控制使用者介面。但由於一些歷史與技術上的因素，並沒有顯著的方法發揮表單的潛力。在下面的指引中，我們將介紹網站表單所有基本面向，包括標記他們的 HTML 結構、設定控制器樣式、驗證數據及將數距提送至伺服器</p>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"參考文章列表","title":"參考文章列表","isH3":false,"content":"<ol>\n  <li><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Learn/Forms/Your_first_form\" class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\">我的第一個 HTML 表單 (en-US)</a></li>\n  <li><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Learn/Forms/How_to_structure_a_web_form\" class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\">如何構建 HTML 表單 (en-US)</a></li>\n  <li><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Learn/Forms/Basic_native_form_controls\" class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\">本機表單控件 (en-US)</a></li>\n  <li>CSS 和 HTML 表單\n    <ol>\n      <li><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Learn/Forms/Styling_web_forms\" class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\">造型 HTML 表單 (en-US)</a></li>\n      <li><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Learn/Forms/Advanced_form_styling\" class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\">HTML 表單高級造型 (en-US)</a></li>\n      <li><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Learn/Forms/Property_compatibility_table_for_form_controls\" class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\">表單控件屬性兼容表 (en-US)</a></li>\n    </ol>\n  </li>\n  <li><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Learn/Forms/Sending_and_retrieving_form_data\" class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\">發送和檢索表單數據 (en-US)</a></li>\n  <li><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Learn/Forms/Form_validation\" class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\">數據表單驗證 (en-US)</a></li>\n  <li><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Learn/Forms/How_to_build_custom_form_controls\" class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\">如何創建自定義表單控件 (en-US)</a></li>\n  <li><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Learn/Forms/Sending_forms_through_JavaScript\" class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\">通過 JavaScript 發送形式 (en-US)</a>\n    <ol>\n      <li><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/FormData/Using_FormData_Objects\" class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\">使用 FORMDATA 對象 (en-US)</a></li>\n    </ol>\n  </li>\n  <li><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Learn/Forms/HTML_forms_in_legacy_browsers\" class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\">在傳統的瀏覽器的 HTML 表單 (en-US)</a></li>\n</ol>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"html_文件","title":"HTML 文件","isH3":false,"content":""}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"html_元素","title":"HTML 元素","isH3":true,"content":"<table>\n  <thead>\n    <tr>\n      <th>HTML 元素</th>\n      <th>元素的 DOM interface</th>\n      <th>說明</th>\n    </tr>\n  </thead>\n  <tbody>\n    <tr>\n      <td><a href=\"/zh-TW/docs/Web/HTML/Element/button\"><code>&lt;button&gt;</code></a></td>\n      <td><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/HTMLButtonElement\"><code>HTMLButtonElement</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></td>\n      <td>該<code>按鈕</code>元素表示一個可點擊的按鈕。</td>\n    </tr>\n    <tr>\n      <td><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/HTML/Element/datalist\"><code>&lt;datalist&gt;</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></td>\n      <td><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/HTMLDataListElement\"><code>HTMLDataListElement</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></td>\n      <td>該數據列表元素包含了一組 <a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/HTML/Element/option\"><code>&lt;option&gt;</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a> 表示對其他表單元素的值可能的選擇要素。</td>\n    </tr>\n    <tr>\n      <td><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/HTML/Element/fieldset\"><code>&lt;fieldset&gt;</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></td>\n      <td><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/HTMLFieldSetElement\"><code>HTMLFieldSetElement</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></td>\n      <td>該字段集是用來在表單中的組數表單元素。</td>\n    </tr>\n    <tr>\n      <td><a href=\"/zh-TW/docs/Web/HTML/Element/form\"><code>&lt;form&gt;</code></a></td>\n      <td><a href=\"/zh-TW/docs/Web/API/HTMLFormElement\"><code>HTMLFormElement</code></a></td>\n      <td>的<code>形式</code>元素表示的文件的一部分，它包含使用戶能夠提交信息給 web 服務器的交互元件。</td>\n    </tr>\n    <tr>\n      <td><a href=\"/zh-TW/docs/Web/HTML/Element/input\"><code>&lt;input&gt;</code></a></td>\n      <td><a href=\"/zh-TW/docs/Web/API/HTMLInputElement\"><code>HTMLInputElement</code></a></td>\n      <td>該 <code>輸入</code>元素用於創建表格的交互式控制。</td>\n    </tr>\n    <tr>\n      <td><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/HTML/Element/keygen\"><code>&lt;keygen&gt;</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></td>\n      <td><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/HTMLKeygenElement\"><code>HTMLKeygenElement</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></td>\n      <td>所述<code>凱基</code>元素存在，以促進生成的密鑰材料，並提交了公開密鑰的作為 HTML 形式的一部分</td>\n    </tr>\n    <tr>\n      <td><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/HTML/Element/label\"><code>&lt;label&gt;</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></td>\n      <td><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/HTMLLabelElement\"><code>HTMLLabelElement</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></td>\n      <td>該<code>標籤</code>元素代表一個項目在用戶界面的標題</td>\n    </tr>\n    <tr>\n      <td><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/HTML/Element/legend\"><code>&lt;legend&gt;</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></td>\n      <td><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/HTMLLegendElement\"><code>HTMLLegendElement</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></td>\n      <td>在<code>傳說</code>元素代表一個標題為其父 <a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/HTML/Element/fieldset\"><code>&lt;fieldset&gt;</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a> 的內容。</td>\n    </tr>\n    <tr>\n      <td><a href=\"/zh-TW/docs/Web/HTML/Element/meter\"><code>&lt;meter&gt;</code></a></td>\n      <td><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/HTMLMeterElement\"><code>HTMLMeterElement</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></td>\n      <td>所述<code>米</code>元素表示一個已知的範圍內的任一標量值或分數值。</td>\n    </tr>\n    <tr>\n      <td><a href=\"/zh-TW/docs/Web/HTML/Element/optgroup\"><code>&lt;optgroup&gt;</code></a></td>\n      <td><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/HTMLOptGroupElement\"><code>HTMLOptGroupElement</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></td>\n      <td>在<code>OPTGROUP</code>元素創建一個 <a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/HTML/Element/select\"><code>&lt;select&gt;</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a> 元素中的一組選項。</td>\n    </tr>\n    <tr>\n      <td><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/HTML/Element/option\"><code>&lt;option&gt;</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></td>\n      <td><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/HTMLOptionElement\"><code>HTMLOptionElement</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></td>\n      <td>在 HTML <code>選項</code>元素用於創建表示 <a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/HTML/Element/select\"><code>&lt;select&gt;</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a> ，一個 <a href=\"/zh-TW/docs/Web/HTML/Element/optgroup\"><code>&lt;optgroup&gt;</code></a> 或 <a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/HTML/Element/datalist\"><code>&lt;datalist&gt;</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a> 元素中的項目的控制。</td>\n    </tr>\n    <tr>\n      <td><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/HTML/Element/output\"><code>&lt;output&gt;</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></td>\n      <td><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/HTMLOutputElement\"><code>HTMLOutputElement</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></td>\n      <td>的<code>輸出</code>元素表示一個計算的結果。</td>\n    </tr>\n    <tr>\n      <td><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/HTML/Element/progress\"><code>&lt;progress&gt;</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></td>\n      <td><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/HTMLProgressElement\"><code>HTMLProgressElement</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></td>\n      <td>的<code>進展</code>元素用於查看任務的完成進度。</td>\n    </tr>\n    <tr>\n      <td><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/HTML/Element/select\"><code>&lt;select&gt;</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></td>\n      <td><a href=\"/zh-TW/docs/Web/API/HTMLSelectElement\"><code>HTMLSelectElement</code></a></td>\n      <td>在<code>選擇</code>元素代表呈現一個選項菜單的控制。</td>\n    </tr>\n    <tr>\n      <td><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/HTML/Element/textarea\"><code>&lt;textarea&gt;</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></td>\n      <td><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/HTMLTextAreaElement\"><code>HTMLTextAreaElement</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></td>\n      <td>該<code>textarea的</code>元素代表多行純文本編輯控制。</td>\n    </tr>\n  </tbody>\n</table>\n<div class=\"notecard note\" id=\"sect1\">\n  <p><strong>備註：</strong> 所有的表單元素，因為所有的 HTML 元素，支持 <a href=\"/zh-TW/docs/Web/API/HTMLElement\"><code>HTMLElement</code></a> DOM 接口。</p>\n</div>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"html_屬性","title":"HTML 屬性","isH3":true,"content":"<table class=\"standard-table\">\n  <thead>\n    <tr>\n      <th>屬性</th>\n      <th>能使用該屬性的 HTML 元素</th>\n      <th>說明</th>\n    </tr>\n  </thead>\n  <tbody>\n    <tr>\n      <td>accept</td>\n      <td><a href=\"/zh-TW/docs/Web/HTML/Element/form\"><code>&lt;form&gt;</code></a>, <a href=\"/zh-TW/docs/Web/HTML/Element/input\"><code>&lt;input&gt;</code></a></td>\n      <td>的類型列表服務器接受，通常是文件類型。</td>\n    </tr>\n    <tr>\n      <td style=\"white-space: nowrap\">accept-charset</td>\n      <td><a href=\"/zh-TW/docs/Web/HTML/Element/form\"><code>&lt;form&gt;</code></a></td>\n      <td>支持的字符集列表。</td>\n    </tr>\n    <tr>\n      <td>action</td>\n      <td><a href=\"/zh-TW/docs/Web/HTML/Element/form\"><code>&lt;form&gt;</code></a></td>\n      <td>一個程序處理通過表單提交的信息的URI。</td>\n    </tr>\n    <tr>\n      <td>autocomplete</td>\n      <td><a href=\"/zh-TW/docs/Web/HTML/Element/form\"><code>&lt;form&gt;</code></a>, <a href=\"/zh-TW/docs/Web/HTML/Element/input\"><code>&lt;input&gt;</code></a></td>\n      <td>指示是否在這個表單控件可以在默認情況下有其值由瀏覽器自動完成。</td>\n    </tr>\n    <tr>\n      <td>autofocus</td>\n      <td>\n        <a href=\"/zh-TW/docs/Web/HTML/Element/button\"><code>&lt;button&gt;</code></a>、\n        <a href=\"/zh-TW/docs/Web/HTML/Element/input\"><code>&lt;input&gt;</code></a>、\n        <a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/HTML/Element/keygen\"><code>&lt;keygen&gt;</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a>、\n        <a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/HTML/Element/select\"><code>&lt;select&gt;</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a>、\n        <a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/HTML/Element/textarea\"><code>&lt;textarea&gt;</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a>\n      </td>\n      <td>該元素應該在頁面加載後自動聚焦。</td>\n    </tr>\n    <tr>\n      <td>challenge</td>\n      <td><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/HTML/Element/keygen\"><code>&lt;keygen&gt;</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></td>\n      <td>即隨著公共密鑰提交的挑戰字符串。</td>\n    </tr>\n    <tr>\n      <td>checked</td>\n      <td><a href=\"/zh-TW/docs/Web/HTML/Element/input\"><code>&lt;input&gt;</code></a></td>\n      <td>指示是否應將元素在頁面加載檢查。</td>\n    </tr>\n    <tr>\n      <td>cols</td>\n      <td><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/HTML/Element/textarea\"><code>&lt;textarea&gt;</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></td>\n      <td>限定在一個textarea的列數。</td>\n    </tr>\n    <tr>\n      <td>data</td>\n      <td><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/HTML/Element/object\"><code>&lt;object&gt;</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></td>\n      <td>指定的資源的URL。</td>\n    </tr>\n    <tr>\n      <td>dirname</td>\n      <td>\n        <a href=\"/zh-TW/docs/Web/HTML/Element/input\"><code>&lt;input&gt;</code></a>,\n        <a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/HTML/Element/textarea\"><code>&lt;textarea&gt;</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a>\n      </td>\n      <td></td>\n    </tr>\n    <tr>\n      <td>disabled</td>\n      <td>\n        <a href=\"/zh-TW/docs/Web/HTML/Element/button\"><code>&lt;button&gt;</code></a>\n        、<a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/HTML/Element/fieldset\"><code>&lt;fieldset&gt;</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a> 、\n        <a href=\"/zh-TW/docs/Web/HTML/Element/input\"><code>&lt;input&gt;</code></a> 、\n        <a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/HTML/Element/keygen\"><code>&lt;keygen&gt;</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a> 、\n        <a href=\"/zh-TW/docs/Web/HTML/Element/optgroup\"><code>&lt;optgroup&gt;</code></a> 、\n        <a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/HTML/Element/option\"><code>&lt;option&gt;</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a> 、\n        <a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/HTML/Element/select\"><code>&lt;select&gt;</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a> 、\n        <a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/HTML/Element/textarea\"><code>&lt;textarea&gt;</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a>\n      </td>\n      <td>表明用戶是否可以與元件進行交互。</td>\n    </tr>\n    <tr>\n      <td>enctype</td>\n      <td><a href=\"/zh-TW/docs/Web/HTML/Element/form\"><code>&lt;form&gt;</code></a></td>\n      <td>定義當表單數據的內容類型<code>的方法</code>是POST。</td>\n    </tr>\n    <tr>\n      <td>for</td>\n      <td>\n        <a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/HTML/Element/label\"><code>&lt;label&gt;</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a>、\n        <a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/HTML/Element/output\"><code>&lt;output&gt;</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a>\n      </td>\n      <td>描述了屬於這一種元素。</td>\n    </tr>\n    <tr>\n      <td>form</td>\n      <td>\n        <a href=\"/zh-TW/docs/Web/HTML/Element/button\"><code>&lt;button&gt;</code></a> 、\n        <a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/HTML/Element/fieldset\"><code>&lt;fieldset&gt;</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a> 、\n        <a href=\"/zh-TW/docs/Web/HTML/Element/input\"><code>&lt;input&gt;</code></a> 、\n        <a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/HTML/Element/keygen\"><code>&lt;keygen&gt;</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a> 、\n        <a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/HTML/Element/label\"><code>&lt;label&gt;</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a> 、\n        <a href=\"/zh-TW/docs/Web/HTML/Element/meter\"><code>&lt;meter&gt;</code></a> 、\n        <a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/HTML/Element/object\"><code>&lt;object&gt;</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a> 、\n        <a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/HTML/Element/output\"><code>&lt;output&gt;</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a> 、\n        <a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/HTML/Element/progress\"><code>&lt;progress&gt;</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a> 、\n        <a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/HTML/Element/select\"><code>&lt;select&gt;</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a> 、\n        <a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/HTML/Element/textarea\"><code>&lt;textarea&gt;</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a>\n      </td>\n      <td>表明是元件的所有者的形式。</td>\n    </tr>\n    <tr>\n      <td>high</td>\n      <td><a href=\"/zh-TW/docs/Web/HTML/Element/meter\"><code>&lt;meter&gt;</code></a></td>\n      <td>表示下界的上限範圍。</td>\n    </tr>\n    <tr>\n      <td>keytype</td>\n      <td><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/HTML/Element/keygen\"><code>&lt;keygen&gt;</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></td>\n      <td>指定鍵所產生的類型。</td>\n    </tr>\n    <tr>\n      <td>list</td>\n      <td><a href=\"/zh-TW/docs/Web/HTML/Element/input\"><code>&lt;input&gt;</code></a></td>\n      <td>標識的預定義的選項的列表，以向用戶建議。</td>\n    </tr>\n    <tr>\n      <td>low</td>\n      <td><a href=\"/zh-TW/docs/Web/HTML/Element/meter\"><code>&lt;meter&gt;</code></a></td>\n      <td>指示上限較低的範圍內。</td>\n    </tr>\n    <tr>\n      <td>max</td>\n      <td>\n        <a href=\"/zh-TW/docs/Web/HTML/Element/input\"><code>&lt;input&gt;</code></a> 、\n        <a href=\"/zh-TW/docs/Web/HTML/Element/meter\"><code>&lt;meter&gt;</code></a> 、\n        <a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/HTML/Element/progress\"><code>&lt;progress&gt;</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a>\n      </td>\n      <td>指示所允許的最大值。</td>\n    </tr>\n    <tr>\n      <td>maxlength</td>\n      <td>\n        <a href=\"/zh-TW/docs/Web/HTML/Element/input\"><code>&lt;input&gt;</code></a> 、\n        <a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/HTML/Element/textarea\"><code>&lt;textarea&gt;</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a>\n      </td>\n      <td>定義了在元件允許的字符的最大數目。</td>\n    </tr>\n    <tr>\n      <td>method</td>\n      <td><a href=\"/zh-TW/docs/Web/HTML/Element/form\"><code>&lt;form&gt;</code></a></td>\n      <td>定義提交表單時使用的HTTP方法。可GET（默認）或POST。</td>\n    </tr>\n    <tr>\n      <td>min</td>\n      <td>\n        <a href=\"/zh-TW/docs/Web/HTML/Element/input\"><code>&lt;input&gt;</code></a> 、\n        <a href=\"/zh-TW/docs/Web/HTML/Element/meter\"><code>&lt;meter&gt;</code></a>\n      </td>\n      <td>指示所允許的最小值。</td>\n    </tr>\n    <tr>\n      <td>multiple</td>\n      <td>\n        <a href=\"/zh-TW/docs/Web/HTML/Element/input\"><code>&lt;input&gt;</code></a>、\n        <a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/HTML/Element/select\"><code>&lt;select&gt;</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a>\n      </td>\n      <td>表示是否多個值所用的類型的輸入可以輸入<code>電子郵件</code>或<code>文件</code>。</td>\n    </tr>\n    <tr>\n      <td>name</td>\n      <td>\n        <a href=\"/zh-TW/docs/Web/HTML/Element/button\"><code>&lt;button&gt;</code></a> 、 <a href=\"/zh-TW/docs/Web/HTML/Element/form\"><code>&lt;form&gt;</code></a>\n        、 <a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/HTML/Element/fieldset\"><code>&lt;fieldset&gt;</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a> 、\n        <a href=\"/zh-TW/docs/Web/HTML/Element/input\"><code>&lt;input&gt;</code></a> 、\n        <a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/HTML/Element/keygen\"><code>&lt;keygen&gt;</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a> 、\n        <a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/HTML/Element/output\"><code>&lt;output&gt;</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a> 、\n        <a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/HTML/Element/select\"><code>&lt;select&gt;</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a> 、\n        <a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/HTML/Element/textarea\"><code>&lt;textarea&gt;</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a>\n      </td>\n      <td>該元素的名稱。例如所使用的服務器，以確定在表單提交的字段。</td>\n    </tr>\n    <tr>\n      <td>novalidate</td>\n      <td><a href=\"/zh-TW/docs/Web/HTML/Element/form\"><code>&lt;form&gt;</code></a></td>\n      <td>此屬性表明，當提交表單應該無法通過驗證。</td>\n    </tr>\n    <tr>\n      <td>optimum</td>\n      <td><a href=\"/zh-TW/docs/Web/HTML/Element/meter\"><code>&lt;meter&gt;</code></a></td>\n      <td>表示最佳數值。</td>\n    </tr>\n    <tr>\n      <td>pattern</td>\n      <td><a href=\"/zh-TW/docs/Web/HTML/Element/input\"><code>&lt;input&gt;</code></a></td>\n      <td>定義一個正則表達式元素的值將針對驗證。</td>\n    </tr>\n    <tr>\n      <td>placeholder</td>\n      <td>\n        <a href=\"/zh-TW/docs/Web/HTML/Element/input\"><code>&lt;input&gt;</code></a>、\n        <a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/HTML/Element/textarea\"><code>&lt;textarea&gt;</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a>\n      </td>\n      <td>提供一個提示什麼可以在字段中輸入的用戶。</td>\n    </tr>\n    <tr>\n      <td>readonly</td>\n      <td>\n        <a href=\"/zh-TW/docs/Web/HTML/Element/input\"><code>&lt;input&gt;</code></a> 、\n        <a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/HTML/Element/textarea\"><code>&lt;textarea&gt;</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a>\n      </td>\n      <td>指示該元素是否可以編輯或沒有。</td>\n    </tr>\n    <tr>\n      <td>required</td>\n      <td>\n        <a href=\"/zh-TW/docs/Web/HTML/Element/input\"><code>&lt;input&gt;</code></a> 、\n        <a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/HTML/Element/select\"><code>&lt;select&gt;</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a>、\n        <a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/HTML/Element/textarea\"><code>&lt;textarea&gt;</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a>\n      </td>\n      <td>指示此元素是否必填。</td>\n    </tr>\n    <tr>\n      <td>rows</td>\n      <td><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/HTML/Element/textarea\"><code>&lt;textarea&gt;</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></td>\n      <td>限定在一個textarea的行數。</td>\n    </tr>\n    <tr>\n      <td>selected</td>\n      <td><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/HTML/Element/option\"><code>&lt;option&gt;</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></td>\n      <td>定義了將在頁面加載所選的值。</td>\n    </tr>\n    <tr>\n      <td>size</td>\n      <td>\n        <a href=\"/zh-TW/docs/Web/HTML/Element/input\"><code>&lt;input&gt;</code></a>、\n        <a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/HTML/Element/select\"><code>&lt;select&gt;</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a>\n      </td>\n      <td>限定了元件的寬度（以像素為單位）。如果該元素的<code>類型</code>的屬性是<code>文本</code>或<code>密碼</code>那麼它的字符數。</td>\n    </tr>\n    <tr>\n      <td>src</td>\n      <td><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/HTML/Element/img\"><code>&lt;img&gt;</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></td>\n      <td>可嵌入內容的URL。</td>\n    </tr>\n    <tr>\n      <td>step</td>\n      <td><a href=\"/zh-TW/docs/Web/HTML/Element/input\"><code>&lt;input&gt;</code></a></td>\n      <td></td>\n    </tr>\n    <tr>\n      <td>target</td>\n      <td><a href=\"/zh-TW/docs/Web/HTML/Element/form\"><code>&lt;form&gt;</code></a></td>\n      <td></td>\n    </tr>\n    <tr>\n      <td>type</td>\n      <td>\n        <a href=\"/zh-TW/docs/Web/HTML/Element/button\"><code>&lt;button&gt;</code></a> 、\n        <a href=\"/zh-TW/docs/Web/HTML/Element/input\"><code>&lt;input&gt;</code></a>\n      </td>\n      <td>限定了元件的類型。</td>\n    </tr>\n    <tr>\n      <td>usemap</td>\n      <td><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/HTML/Element/img\"><code>&lt;img&gt;</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></td>\n      <td></td>\n    </tr>\n    <tr>\n      <td>value</td>\n      <td>\n        <a href=\"/zh-TW/docs/Web/HTML/Element/button\"><code>&lt;button&gt;</code></a>、\n        <a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/HTML/Element/option\"><code>&lt;option&gt;</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a>、\n        <a href=\"/zh-TW/docs/Web/HTML/Element/input\"><code>&lt;input&gt;</code></a>、\n        <a href=\"/zh-TW/docs/Web/HTML/Element/meter\"><code>&lt;meter&gt;</code></a>、\n        <a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/HTML/Element/progress\"><code>&lt;progress&gt;</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a>\n      </td>\n      <td>定義了將被顯示在頁面上的負載元件的默認值。</td>\n    </tr>\n    <tr>\n      <td>wrap</td>\n      <td><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/HTML/Element/textarea\"><code>&lt;textarea&gt;</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></td>\n      <td>指示文本是否應被包裹或沒有。</td>\n    </tr>\n  </tbody>\n</table>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"規範性引用文件","title":"規範性引用文件","isH3":true,"content":"<ul>\n  <li><a href=\"https://www.w3.org/html/wg/drafts/html/master/forms.html#forms\" class=\"external\" rel=\" noopener\">W3C HTML 5.1 規範（表格）</a></li>\n  <li><a href=\"https://www.whatwg.org/specs/web-apps/current-work/multipage/forms.html#forms\" class=\"external\" rel=\" noopener\">WHATWG HTML 生活水平（表格）</a></li>\n</ul>"}}],"toc":[{"text":"參考文章列表","id":"參考文章列表"},{"text":"HTML 文件","id":"html_文件"}],"summary":"這篇指南提供了一系列的文章，幫你掌握 HTML 表單的基本知識。對於與使用者互動，網站表單是一項十分有力的工具，最常使用於用戶數據蒐集，或控制使用者介面。但由於一些歷史與技術上的因素，並沒有顯著的方法發揮表單的潛力。在下面的指引中，我們將介紹網站表單所有基本面向，包括標記他們的 HTML 結構、設定控制器樣式、驗證數據及將數距提送至伺服器","popularity":0.0002,"modified":"2022-10-01T03:41:16.000Z","other_translations":[{"title":"Web forms — Working with user data","locale":"en-US","native":"English (US)"},{"title":"Formularios en HTML5","locale":"es","native":"Español"},{"title":"Formulaires HTML","locale":"fr","native":"Français"},{"title":"HTML フォーム","locale":"ja","native":"日本語"},{"title":"HTML 폼 가이드","locale":"ko","native":"한국어"},{"title":"Formulários da Web - Trabalhando com dados do usuário","locale":"pt-BR","native":"Português (do Brasil)"},{"title":"Руководство по HTML-формам","locale":"ru","native":"Русский"},{"title":"Web 表单指南","locale":"zh-CN","native":"中文 (简体)"}],"source":{"folder":"zh-tw/learn/forms","github_url":"https://github.com/mdn/translated-content/blob/main/files/zh-tw/learn/forms/index.md","last_commit_url":"https://github.com/mdn/translated-content/commit/921c46a374ab0a9f4cc809af0370f8c412e54701","filename":"index.md"},"parents":[{"uri":"/zh-TW/docs/Learn","title":"學習該如何開發 Web"},{"uri":"/zh-TW/docs/Learn/Forms","title":"網站表單-與數據合作"}],"pageTitle":"網站表單-與數據合作 - 學習該如何開發 Web | MDN","noIndexing":false}}